Deploy on Heroku and Git

1. Setup Git and commit files
    - git init
    - git status
    - git add .
    - git commit -m 
2. ignore node_modules
    - touch .gitignore
    - node_modules
3. Setup a Github repo and push 
    - git remote add origin git@github.com:jnthns/node-chat-app.git
    - git push -u origin master
4. Setup a Heroku app and push
    - heroku create {{app name}}
    - git push heroku master